    Deprecated. 
    the PostgreSQL RDF store is no longer supported and will be removed in a future Sesame release. Consider switching to a different SAIL backend.

public class PgSqlStore
extends RdbmsStore
    A convenient way to initialise a PostgreSQL RDF store.
